title: New: Sans Parents – Dead End
body:
It’s probably my recent obsession with Netflix’s Stranger Things that has in part got me going crazy over 80’s-esque music again.

This new track from Brisbane’s **Sans Parents** could pretty much be lifted straight from the TV show’s soundtrack, fitting in nicely alongside the likes of Modern English and Television. Check out _Dead End_ below.

Like this? Follow our [On Repeat Playlist](https://open.spotify.com/user/crackintheroad/playlist/1UB6gJIZpmiO0H2zmSbg02) for a handpicked selection of the very best in new music; updated weekly.
